This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=3773

Awesome plugin to view the lyrics of your favorite song without leaving VIM!

1 - Install
Put lyrics.vim in your ~/.vim/plugin folder.

2 - How to use
:Lyrics -> show the lyrics of the current song played in Rhythmbox.
:SearchLyrics -> input: song-artist, show the lyrics of the song of your choice

3 - Dependencies
- wget in your path to download the lyrics from www.lyrics.com
- Rhythmbox for the Lyrics command
- vim 7

4 - License
GPLv2

Tested on Ubuntu 10.04.
